{"number":92,"ayahs":[{"numberInSurah":1,"arabic":" وَٱلَّيْلِ إِذَا يَغْشَىٰ","translation":"By the night when it covers","transliteration":"Wallayli itha yaghsha","page":595},{"numberInSurah":2,"arabic":"وَٱلنَّهَارِ إِذَا تَجَلَّىٰ","translation":"And [by] the day when it appears","transliteration":"Wannahari itha tajalla","page":595},{"numberInSurah":3,"arabic":"وَمَا خَلَقَ ٱلذَّكَرَ وَٱلْأُنثَىٰٓ","translation":"And [by] He who created the male and female,","transliteration":"Wama khalaqa aththakarawal-ontha","page":595},{"numberInSurah":4,"arabic":"إِنَّ سَعْيَكُمْ لَشَتَّىٰ","translation":"Indeed, your efforts are diverse.","transliteration":"Inna saAAyakum lashatta","page":595},{"numberInSurah":5,"arabic":"فَأَمَّا مَنْ أَعْطَىٰ وَٱتَّقَىٰ","translation":"As for he who gives and fears Allāh","transliteration":"Faamma man aAAta wattaqa","page":595},{"numberInSurah":6,"arabic":"وَصَدَّقَ بِٱلْحُسْنَىٰ","translation":"And believes in the best [reward],","transliteration":"Wasaddaqa bilhusna","page":595},{"numberInSurah":7,"arabic":"فَسَنُيَسِّرُهُۥ لِلْيُسْرَىٰ","translation":"We will ease him toward ease.","transliteration":"Fasanuyassiruhu lilyusra","page":595},{"numberInSurah":8,"arabic":"وَأَمَّا مَنۢ بَخِلَ وَٱسْتَغْنَىٰ","translation":"But as for he who withholds and considers himself free of need","transliteration":"Waamma man bakhila wastaghna","page":595},{"numberInSurah":9,"arabic":"وَكَذَّبَ بِٱلْحُسْنَىٰ","translation":"And denies the best [reward],","transliteration":"Wakaththaba bilhusna","page":595},{"numberInSurah":10,"arabic":"فَسَنُيَسِّرُهُۥ لِلْعُسْرَىٰ","translation":"We will ease him toward difficulty.","transliteration":"Fasanuyassiruhu lilAAusra","page":595},{"numberInSurah":11,"arabic":"وَمَا يُغْنِى عَنْهُ مَالُهُۥٓ إِذَا تَرَدَّىٰٓ","translation":"And what will his wealth avail him when he falls?","transliteration":"Wama yughnee AAanhu maluhu ithataradda","page":595},{"numberInSurah":12,"arabic":"إِنَّ عَلَيْنَا لَلْهُدَىٰ","translation":"Indeed, [incumbent] upon Us is guidance.","transliteration":"Inna AAalayna lalhuda","page":595},{"numberInSurah":13,"arabic":"وَإِنَّ لَنَا لَلْـَٔاخِرَةَ وَٱلْأُولَىٰ","translation":"And indeed, to us belongs the Hereafter and the first [life].","transliteration":"Wa-inna lana lal-akhirata wal-oola","page":595},{"numberInSurah":14,"arabic":"فَأَنذَرْتُكُمْ نَارًا تَلَظَّىٰ","translation":"So I have warned you of a Fire which is blazing.","transliteration":"Faanthartukum naran talaththa","page":595},{"numberInSurah":15,"arabic":"لَا يَصْلَىٰهَآ إِلَّا ٱلْأَشْقَى","translation":"None will [enter to] burn therein except the most wretched one","transliteration":"La yaslaha illaal-ashqa","page":596},{"numberInSurah":16,"arabic":"ٱلَّذِى كَذَّبَ وَتَوَلَّىٰ","translation":"Who had denied and turned away.","transliteration":"Allathee kaththaba watawalla","page":596},{"numberInSurah":17,"arabic":"وَسَيُجَنَّبُهَا ٱلْأَتْقَى","translation":"But the righteous one will avoid it","transliteration":"Wasayujannabuha al-atqa","page":596},{"numberInSurah":18,"arabic":"ٱلَّذِى يُؤْتِى مَالَهُۥ يَتَزَكَّىٰ","translation":"[He] who gives [from] his wealth to purify himself","transliteration":"Allathee yu/tee malahuyatazakka","page":596},{"numberInSurah":19,"arabic":"وَمَا لِأَحَدٍ عِندَهُۥ مِن نِّعْمَةٍ تُجْزَىٰٓ","translation":"And not [giving] for anyone who has [done him] a favor to be rewarded","transliteration":"Wama li-ahadin AAindahu minniAAmatin tujza","page":596},{"numberInSurah":20,"arabic":"إِلَّا ٱبْتِغَآءَ وَجْهِ رَبِّهِ ٱلْأَعْلَىٰ","translation":"But only seeking the face [i.e., acceptance] of his Lord, Most High.","transliteration":"Illa ibtighaa wajhi rabbihial-aAAla","page":596},{"numberInSurah":21,"arabic":"وَلَسَوْفَ يَرْضَىٰ","translation":"And he is going to be satisfied.","transliteration":"Walasawfa yarda","page":596}]}